  "text": "The aforementioned process of accumulated swaging and bundling (ASB) was adopted to obtain a composite material of an entirely ufg microstructure [CITATION_1] . By this means a wire is formed whose dimensions can be adjusted in a wide range. The latter, however, depends on the facilities that are to hand as well as on the size of the initial composite.",
